16:14.122 --> 16:17.025
to seize 
the Administrative Center’s property. 


16:17.025 --> 16:20.395
However, when they tried 
to seize the Bethel complex, 


16:20.395 --> 16:24.400
they found out that it legally belonged, 
not to the Administrative Center, 


16:24.400 --> 16:28.403
but actually to the Watch Tower Bible 
and Tract Society of Pennsylvania 


16:28.403 --> 16:30.405
and that for 17 years, 


16:30.405 --> 16:33.808
the Administrative Center 
had been merely a tenant. 


16:33.808 --> 16:37.813
Since the Pennsylvania Corporation 
hadn’t been banned, 


16:37.813 --> 16:41.816
this created a legal obstacle 
for the government in seizing our property.


16:41.817 --> 16:44.587
So, what argument 
did the government use 


16:44.587 --> 16:48.000
to try to justify the seizure 
of the branch property?


16:49.825 --> 16:53.495
Well, the government was trying to prove 
that the transfer of title of the property 


16:53.495 --> 16:57.398
to the Pennsylvania Corporation 
17 years ago wasn’t valid 


16:57.398 --> 16:59.401
and that the Bethel property 


16:59.402 --> 17:02.170
still really belonged
 to the Administrative Center, 


17:02.170 --> 17:05.707
and therefore it was 
fair game for them to seize it.


17:05.707 --> 17:08.577
Richard, 
can you tell us what it was like 


17:08.577 --> 17:12.000
to be there in the courtroom 
for this very historic hearing?


17:13.115 --> 17:16.518
Well, a couple of things 
really impressed me very much. 


17:16.518 --> 17:20.855
One was the courage of the local brothers 
and sisters who came to the hearing 


17:20.855 --> 17:25.527
despite the ban just to support 
the brothers presenting our case. 


17:25.527 --> 17:30.532
It was truly a remarkable demonstration 
of strong faith and determination. 


