The hearing was held 
in a small, drab room 


17:33.268 --> 17:37.705
in Sestroretsk, a town not far 
from the former Bethel facility. 


17:37.705 --> 17:41.042
There was barely room 
for everyone to fit inside. 


17:41.042 --> 17:44.647
Our attorneys and the prosecutors 
were literally two feet apart, 


17:44.647 --> 17:47.415
facing each other over a small table. 


17:47.415 --> 17:50.785
The brothers and sisters 
crammed into any space they could find, 


17:50.785 --> 17:54.122
some even sitting inside the barred cell 


17:54.122 --> 17:56.492
reserved for criminal defendants.


17:56.492 --> 18:00.195
Well now, Richard, what can you 
tell us about the hearing itself? 


18:00.195 --> 18:02.430
What actually took place in the courtroom?


18:02.430 --> 18:05.833
Well, I knew from meeting 
with them the night before 


18:05.833 --> 18:08.770
how well our attorneys 
prepared for this case 


18:08.770 --> 18:10.938
and how hard they worked on it. 


18:10.938 --> 18:12.941
And to see them both


18:12.942 --> 18:15.644
—one a relatively young brother—
courageously stand up 


18:15.643 --> 18:17.880
and defend the interests of Jehovah’s people, 


18:17.880 --> 18:20.215
it was really an amazing sight. 


18:20.215 --> 18:23.152
They had real conviction and passion. 


18:23.152 --> 18:27.155
They demonstrated unequivocally 
that according to Russian law, 


18:27.155 --> 18:30.858
the international business law, 


18:30.858 --> 18:34.596
and the provisions 
of the European Convention on Human Rights 


18:34.597 --> 18:36.899
that they were squarely 
in our favor 


18:36.898 --> 18:40.568
and that to seize our property 
was not only legally wrong 


18:40.568 --> 18:43.271
but it was really morally wrong. 


18:43.272 --> 18:48.277
The prosecutors, on the other hand, 
appeared to be not long out of high school 


18:48.277 --> 18:52.547
and limited themselves to reading 
a few short prewritten statements 


18:52.547 --> 18:55.784
and asked no questions during the hearing.


18:55.783 --> 18:58.386
Well now, Richard, what was it like 


18:58.387 --> 19:02.357
when the decision 
was finally read in the courtroom?


19:02.357 --> 19:05.760
Well, I don’t think the decision 
was really a surprise to anyone. 


19:05.760 --> 19:08.130
However, it seemed to me that the judge 


19:08.130 --> 19:11.098
was very uncomfortable reading that verdict. 


19:11.098 --> 19:13.301
At the end, 
she announced that there would be 


19:13.302 --> 19:15.504
30 days to file an appeal. 


19:15.503 --> 19:18.306
Now, the spirit of the brothers 
and sisters leaving the courtroom 


19:18.307 --> 19:20.309
was somber at first. 


19:20.308 --> 19:23.645
But once we were out in the hallway, 
the conversations got going; 


19:23.645 --> 19:26.415
the brothers and sisters 
began congratulating the attorneys 


19:26.415 --> 19:28.450
for the fine witness they had given. 


19:28.450 --> 19:31.453
Once again, they were all smiling, 
laughing, hugging, 


19:31.453 --> 19:33.655
and even giving little gifts to one another. 


19:33.655 --> 19:37.000
They were once again just happy 
to be together serving Jehovah.


19:38.160 --> 19:40.162
Well, then, what happens now? 


19:40.162 --> 19:42.164
Where do we go from here, Richard?


19:42.163 --> 19:47.001
Well, the brothers are planning 
to file an appeal within the given time. 


19:47.002 --> 19:49.972
And if this first appeal goes against us, 


19:49.972 --> 19:52.240
then the property 
will be seized by the government 


19:52.240 --> 19:54.375
and used for other purposes. 


19:54.375 --> 19:59.380
However, further appeals, possibly even 
to the European Court of Human Rights, 


19:59.380 --> 20:02.050
will be pursued. 


20:02.050 --> 20:05.787
Richard, thank you very, very much 
for giving us that report. 


20:05.787 --> 20:07.789
And even more, 
we want to thank you 


20:07.788 --> 20:11.091
for the courage that you 
demonstrated in going to Russia 


20:11.092 --> 20:13.662
to stand with our brothers 
during that hearing.


20:13.662 --> 20:16.365
It really was my privilege. 
Thank you.


20:16.365 --> 20:19.200
However, 
the seizure of our other properties 


20:19.200 --> 20:22.270
has already begun in Russia. 


20:22.270 --> 20:26.508
For example, 
on December 14, 2017, 


20:26.508 --> 20:28.976
just after 9:00 a.m., 


20:28.977 --> 20:32.414
about 40 people, 
including police and others, 


20:32.413 --> 20:35.683
appeared outside the Assembly Hall 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses 


20:35.683 --> 20:37.685
in St. Petersburg. 


20:37.685 --> 20:40.522
Some of the men were armed 
with automatic weapons, 


20:40.522 --> 20:43.725
and others had the tools 
needed to forcibly enter 


20:43.725 --> 20:46.462
the locked Assembly Hall compound. 


20:46.462 --> 20:48.997
Thankfully, none of our brothers 


20:48.997 --> 20:52.200
were inside the Assembly Hall 
during this raid. 


20:52.200 --> 20:54.970
Russian news agencies have reported 


20:54.970 --> 20:59.107
that based on the Russian Supreme 
Court ruling earlier this year, 


20:59.107 --> 21:01.610
the government has seized the property 


21:01.610 --> 21:04.312
and has transferred it 
to the neighboring medical center 


21:04.312 --> 21:06.849
for use as a lecture hall. 


21:06.848 --> 21:11.118
They have already posted 
a new sign on the gate.


21:11.118 --> 21:13.588
In addition to these actions, 


21:13.588 --> 21:17.091
you may be wondering 
about our Brother Dennis Christensen 


21:17.092 --> 21:19.260
who has been in pretrial detention 


21:19.260 --> 21:23.232
since May 25, 2017. 


21:23.232 --> 21:28.104
The court has extended 
his pretrial detention several times. 


21:28.103 --> 21:32.673
Most recently, on December 22, 2017, 


21:32.673 --> 21:35.510
the court extended his detention 


21:35.510 --> 21:39.313
until February 23, 2018. 


21:39.313 --> 21:43.485
The authorities are allowing 
Brother Christensen’s wife 


21:43.485 --> 21:45.853
to visit him now twice a month. 


21:45.853 --> 21:49.323
We expect that his trial 
will begin sometime 


21:49.323 --> 21:52.160
in the coming weeks. 


21:52.160 --> 21:54.228
What can we say, brothers, 


21:54.228 --> 21:58.900
about this attack on pure worship in Russia? 


21:58.900 --> 22:03.272
Jehovah foretold 
that during Christ’s presence, 


22:03.272 --> 22:07.175
‘the kings of the earth and high officials 


22:07.175 --> 22:12.180
would take their stand 
against Jehovah and his anointed one.’ 


22:12.180 --> 22:17.185
We find that in Psalm 2:1-3. 


22:17.185 --> 22:21.857
Thus, we are not surprised 
to see this direct attack 


22:21.857 --> 22:23.859
on Jehovah’s name; 


22:23.858 --> 22:26.260
his precious Word, the Bible; 


22:26.260 --> 22:30.265
and his faithful worshippers on this earth. 


22:30.265 --> 22:35.103
We must keep in our minds 
the warning from our Lord Jesus 


22:35.103 --> 22:40.975
when he said at Matthew 10:17-22: 


22:40.975 --> 22:44.145
“Be on your guard against men, 


22:44.145 --> 22:47.515
“for they will hand you over to local courts 


22:47.515 --> 22:50.785
“and they will scourge 
you in their synagogues. 


22:50.785 --> 22:55.723
“And you will be brought 
before governors and kings for my sake, 


22:55.723 --> 22:59.560
“for a witness to them and the nations. 


22:59.560 --> 23:03.665
“However, when they hand you over, 


23:03.665 --> 23:08.670
“do not become anxious 
about how or what you are to speak, 


23:08.670 --> 23:12.840
“for what you are to speak 
will be given you in that hour; 


23:12.840 --> 23:17.012
“for the ones speaking are not just you, 


23:17.012 --> 23:22.017
“but it is the spirit of your Father 
that speaks by you. 


23:22.017 --> 23:26.522
“Further, brother will hand 
brother over to death, 


23:26.522 --> 23:28.957
“and a father his child, 


23:28.957 --> 23:31.894
“and children will rise up against parents 


23:31.893 --> 23:34.361
“and will have them put to death. 


23:34.362 --> 23:37.999
“And you will be hated by all people 


23:37.998 --> 23:40.535
“on account of my name, 


23:40.535 --> 23:44.738
“but the one who has endured to the end 


23:44.738 --> 23:47.108
will be saved.”


23:47.108 --> 23:50.145
Yes, as Jesus said, 


23:50.145 --> 23:55.150
all who endure faithfully 
will ultimately be saved. 


23:55.150 --> 23:57.952
Jehovah stated through his prophet 


23:57.952 --> 24:01.222
at Ezekiel 39:7: 


24:01.222 --> 24:04.292
“The nations will have to know 


24:04.292 --> 24:07.729
that I am Jehovah.” 


24:07.728 --> 24:12.733
Soon, Jehovah will act 
in behalf of all his servants who, 


24:12.733 --> 24:16.638
despite opposition 
and adverse circumstances, 


24:16.638 --> 24:21.643
prove that they are truly 
“a people for his name.”


24:21.643 --> 24:24.278
This is JW Broadcasting 


24:24.278 --> 24:34.506
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

